	{SITE_TITLE}. All rights reserved.
	<div
		class="decoration-none flex flex-row gap-x-3 text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 dark:hover:text-slate-300"
	>
		<a href="https://github.com/DEVACA" target="_blank">
			<span class="sr-only">Go to {SITE_TITLE}'s GitHub repo</span>
			<svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" class="h-8 w-8"
